{
  "lines": [
    {
      "key": "20.0",
      "line_index": 20,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "250bdda9",
      "speaker": "ベス",
      "ja": "全然ダメ……内容が頭に入ってこないわ……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "22.0",
      "line_index": 22,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "c616d695",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "魔法の勉強を始めて数時間……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "23.0",
      "line_index": 23,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "f8d5d6b1",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "休むことなく勉強を続けていたせいで、さすがに疲労感を覚える。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "27.0",
      "line_index": 27,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "7c4676b9",
      "speaker": "ベス",
      "ja": "テストまであまり時間がありませんのに……どうすればいいのかしら……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "33.0",
      "line_index": 33,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "65bb4f06",
      "speaker": "ベス",
      "ja": "あっ……そういえば以前オーロラさんが言ってた特急の栄養剤、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "33.2",
      "line_index": 33,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "65bb4f06",
      "speaker": "ベス",
      "ja": "それがあればもしかして……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "36.0",
      "line_index": 36,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "a668e3b0",
      "speaker": "ベス",
      "ja": "でもあの話本当なのかしら……あの男の精液が特別な栄養剤って……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "36.2",
      "line_index": 36,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "a668e3b0",
      "speaker": "ベス",
      "ja": "その……いい人、だとは思いますけど……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "38.0",
      "line_index": 38,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "362e85e1",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "{G_PlayerName} のことを思い浮かべ、胸がとくんと高鳴る。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "41.0",
      "line_index": 41,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "2be098c3",
      "speaker": "ベス",
      "ja": "それにしても精液、なんて……どうしてそんなものが……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "43.0",
      "line_index": 43,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "2efc33e6",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "精液がどんなものなのか、本でしか知らない。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "44.0",
      "line_index": 44,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "ab23d165",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "ただそれを出す方法を思い出すだけで、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "44.2",
      "line_index": 44,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "ab23d165",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "顔から火がでそうになるほど熱くなってしまう。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "48.0",
      "line_index": 48,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "e4b73a26",
      "speaker": "ベス",
      "ja": "でもこのままでは埒があきませんわ……。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "48.2",
      "line_index": 48,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "e4b73a26",
      "speaker": "ベス",
      "ja": "恥ずかしいけど、もしあの話が本当なら……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "55.0",
      "line_index": 55,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "930ea7b0",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "今日は疲れた……そろそろ寝るか",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "58.0",
      "line_index": 58,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "86f71691",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "──トントン",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "61.0",
      "line_index": 61,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "c500e1cc",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "──ん？　こんな時間に誰だろう？　はーい、誰？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "66.0",
      "line_index": 66,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "1385a2fd",
      "speaker": "ベス",
      "ja": "わ、私よ……ベスよ。今時間あるかしら？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "69.0",
      "line_index": 69,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "371f554c",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "こんな時間に珍しい来客だな……開いてるよ、勝手に入って",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "75.0",
      "line_index": 75,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "18120773",
      "speaker": "ベス",
      "ja": "よかった、まだ起きていましたのね",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "77.0",
      "line_index": 77,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "604185d7",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "部屋の中に静かに入ってきたベス。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "78.0",
      "line_index": 78,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "e83afc1f",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "心なしか頬が紅く染まり、チラチラとこちらをみつめてくる。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "81.0",
      "line_index": 81,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "cdd58da8",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "それでこんな夜分遅くに何か用事？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "86.0",
      "line_index": 86,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "8ed7c104",
      "speaker": "ベス",
      "ja": "え、ええ……大事な用事がありまして……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "86.2",
      "line_index": 86,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "8ed7c104",
      "speaker": "ベス",
      "ja": "その……オーロラさんから聞いたのですけど、その……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "89.0",
      "line_index": 89,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "4d3edc39",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "（何だろう？　妙に恥ずかしがってるけど……。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "89.2",
      "line_index": 89,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "4d3edc39",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": " いつもは勝気で言いたいことはズバズバ言ってくるのに……珍しいな）",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "95.0",
      "line_index": 95,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "bc04a8c8",
      "speaker": "ベス",
      "ja": "うううう……！　恥ずかしがっている場合ではありませんわっ！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "95.2",
      "line_index": 95,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "bc04a8c8",
      "speaker": "ベス",
      "ja": "その……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "95.5",
      "line_index": 95,
      "inline_index": 5,
      "line_hash": "bc04a8c8",
      "speaker": "ベス",
      "ja": "あ、あなたの、せっせせせ、せーえきっ！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "95.7",
      "line_index": 95,
      "inline_index": 7,
      "line_hash": "bc04a8c8",
      "speaker": "ベス",
      "ja": "と、特別だと聞いて……！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "98.0",
      "line_index": 98,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "4e346dbb",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "えっ！？　せー……なに？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "104.0",
      "line_index": 104,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "2f9cf56e",
      "speaker": "ベス",
      "ja": "精液よ精液！！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "104.2",
      "line_index": 104,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "2f9cf56e",
      "speaker": "ベス",
      "ja": "貴方がその、お、おち……股間から出す真っ白な物！！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "104.4",
      "line_index": 104,
      "inline_index": 4,
      "line_hash": "2f9cf56e",
      "speaker": "ベス",
      "ja": "それが身体に良いって聞いたの！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "108.0",
      "line_index": 108,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "e5ec4af3",
      "speaker": "ベス",
      "ja": "す、少しでいいからその、私にも分けてくださるかしら……？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "108.2",
      "line_index": 108,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "e5ec4af3",
      "speaker": "ベス",
      "ja": "べ、別にヘンな意味は無くて……！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "108.4",
      "line_index": 108,
      "inline_index": 4,
      "line_hash": "e5ec4af3",
      "speaker": "ベス",
      "ja": "少しでも魔法の勉強を捗らせるために必要でっ！！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "110.0",
      "line_index": 110,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "12c00ce0",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "ベスは顔を真っ赤にしながら叫ぶ。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "112.0",
      "line_index": 112,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "62738010",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "最初は冗談かと思っていたが、その瞳は真剣そのものだ。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "113.0",
      "line_index": 113,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "95692915",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "本当に俺のを求めている……それがはっきりと伝わってくる。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "116.0",
      "line_index": 116,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "b3f70d62",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "……ベスも……？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "116.2",
      "line_index": 116,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "b3f70d62",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "どうして俺のがそんな特別とか……別に普通だと思うんだけど……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "116.4",
      "line_index": 116,
      "inline_index": 4,
      "line_hash": "b3f70d62",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "一体全体どうしてそんな話になっているんだよ",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "121.0",
      "line_index": 121,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "66f2a642",
      "speaker": "ベス",
      "ja": "ベス”も”？　それってどういう意味かしら？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "124.0",
      "line_index": 124,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "7b2b5b5e",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "──あっ！？　そ、その……深い意味は……！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "130.0",
      "line_index": 130,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "b2564a7c",
      "speaker": "ベス",
      "ja": "もしかして私以外にも……？　どうなのよっ！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "133.0",
      "line_index": 133,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "2a6fe123",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "あ、ああ……その……さっき他の娘にも同じようにせがまれて仕方なく……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "139.0",
      "line_index": 139,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "9d157322",
      "speaker": "ベス",
      "ja": "な、なんですって！？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "139.2",
      "line_index": 139,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "9d157322",
      "speaker": "ベス",
      "ja": "わ、私というものがありながら他の娘にも！？は、ハレンチですわ……！！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "145.0",
      "line_index": 145,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "1ac975ed",
      "speaker": "ベス",
      "ja": "これは由々しき事態ですわ……まさか他の娘たちに先を越されるなんて……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "148.0",
      "line_index": 148,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "3543be31",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "えっと、その……でも俺とベスは別に特別な関係でも無いし……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "155.0",
      "line_index": 155,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "2d6f878",
      "speaker": "ベス",
      "ja": "────！！！　ひ、人の気も知らないで……！　この唐変木！！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "155.2",
      "line_index": 155,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "2d6f878",
      "speaker": "ベス",
      "ja": "もうこうなったら他の娘が目に入らないようにしないといけませんわね……！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "159.0",
      "line_index": 159,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "d9b1049f",
      "speaker": "ベス",
      "ja": "私以外では出せないようにしないと……！！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "162.0",
      "line_index": 162,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "1f3ff6b7",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "うわっ！　ちょ……！　どこに手突っ込んで……止めろって！！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "165.0",
      "line_index": 165,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "e304145c",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "ベスは強引に俺のズボンの中に手を突っ込むと、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "165.2",
      "line_index": 165,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "e304145c",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "細く小さな指で肉棒を弄り始める。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "171.0",
      "line_index": 171,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "cb7762e8",
      "speaker": "ベス",
      "ja": "むむ……あまり硬くなっていませんわね……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "171.2",
      "line_index": 171,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "cb7762e8",
      "speaker": "ベス",
      "ja": "殿方はここを硬くしてくださるものだときいていましたのに……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "174.0",
      "line_index": 174,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "1f2a9f3c",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "そ、そりゃいきなりなんて……それにさっき……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "177.0",
      "line_index": 177,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "76fc87b8",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "たくさん出して、と言いかけて慌てて口を紡ぐ。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "180.0",
      "line_index": 180,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "584a3c72",
      "speaker": "ベス",
      "ja": "どうすればすぐに硬くできますの？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "180.4",
      "line_index": 180,
      "inline_index": 4,
      "line_hash": "584a3c72",
      "speaker": "ベス",
      "ja": "私には時間がありませんの……早く硬くしてくださいましっ",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "183.0",
      "line_index": 183,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "83272383",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "そ、そんなこと言われても……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "183.2",
      "line_index": 183,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "83272383",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "ああ、もっと強い刺激……ベスのそこを使わせてもらうとか……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "186.0",
      "line_index": 186,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "91bcd535",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "ベスの股間を指さすと、すぐに俺の考えを理解したのか",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "186.2",
      "line_index": 186,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "91bcd535",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "赤かった顔がさらに真っ赤になっていく。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "191.0",
      "line_index": 191,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "a3792e96",
      "speaker": "ベス",
      "ja": "あ、あそこ……！？　ですってぇ！？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "191.2",
      "line_index": 191,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "a3792e96",
      "speaker": "ベス",
      "ja": "そ、そんなの恥ずかしすぎますわ……！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "191.4",
      "line_index": 191,
      "inline_index": 4,
      "line_hash": "a3792e96",
      "speaker": "ベス",
      "ja": "でも時間が……それにうかうかしていられないわ……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "195.0",
      "line_index": 195,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "863c52f4",
      "speaker": "ベス",
      "ja": "わ、わかりましたわ……！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "195.2",
      "line_index": 195,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "863c52f4",
      "speaker": "ベス",
      "ja": "貴方がそれで股間を大きくするなら……射精するなら……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "195.4",
      "line_index": 195,
      "inline_index": 4,
      "line_hash": "863c52f4",
      "speaker": "ベス",
      "ja": "この身を捧げますわ……！！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "209.0",
      "line_index": 209,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "8c08d228",
      "speaker": "ベス",
      "ja": "はう……！♥　な、なんて熱いですの……んんっ♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "212.0",
      "line_index": 212,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "945f5062",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "（うわ……これ想像以上にいいかも……！！）",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "215.0",
      "line_index": 215,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "587788c0",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "思いつきに近い形で要求した素股。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "216.0",
      "line_index": 216,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "5690796a",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "しかしベスのスベスベでむちむちした太ももが思いの外快感をもたらす。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "218.0",
      "line_index": 218,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "9c0cd0b",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "そして割れ目からじんわりと熱と滑りが伝わり、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "218.2",
      "line_index": 218,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "9c0cd0b",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "それがさらに肉棒を気持ち良くしてくる。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "221.0",
      "line_index": 221,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "75cbb142",
      "speaker": "ベス",
      "ja": "うう……こ、これでちゃんと精液が出せるんでしょうね？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "224.0",
      "line_index": 224,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "4d5273e8",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "たぶん……大丈夫だと思う",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "228.0",
      "line_index": 228,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "bfadc5db",
      "speaker": "ベス",
      "ja": "たぶんじゃ困りますわ……！　確約してくださいまし……！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "231.0",
      "line_index": 231,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "c63294ec",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "うおっ！　そ、そんな足動かさないでくれ……！！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "235.0",
      "line_index": 235,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "e86af155",
      "speaker": "ベス",
      "ja": "あっ！？　も、もしかして痛かったですの？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "238.0",
      "line_index": 238,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "66d9df88",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "い、いや、全然痛くないから。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "238.2",
      "line_index": 238,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "66d9df88",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "ベスのおまんこと太もものお陰で硬くなってきてるから",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "242.0",
      "line_index": 242,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "4c061d30",
      "speaker": "ベス",
      "ja": "そ、そう……？　それなら良かったですわ。それですぐに射精しますの……？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "245.0",
      "line_index": 245,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "2a6046d",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "このままじゃさすがに……出やすいように動くけどいいかな？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "249.0",
      "line_index": 249,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "55064e99",
      "speaker": "ベス",
      "ja": "動く……このまま……？　それってあそこ擦られるんじゃ……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "252.0",
      "line_index": 252,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "e1e8c78a",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "まあそうなるかな……嫌なら……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "256.0",
      "line_index": 256,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "70370451",
      "speaker": "ベス",
      "ja": "い、いえ……！　出してもらわないとテストに困りますのっ！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "256.2",
      "line_index": 256,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "70370451",
      "speaker": "ベス",
      "ja": "この身を捧げると言った以上、何でも受け入れますわ",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "259.0",
      "line_index": 259,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "c8d68271",
      "speaker": "ベス",
      "ja": "さ、さあいつでも来なさい……！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "261.0",
      "line_index": 261,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "7e992dd9",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "言葉尻は強気だが、緊張に僅かに身体を震わせるベス。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "262.0",
      "line_index": 262,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "5374c771",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "そんなベスを少しでも落ち着かせようとそっと抱きしめる。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "265.0",
      "line_index": 265,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "b17da9dc",
      "speaker": "ベス",
      "ja": "うう、その……お胸、そんなに触れると……。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "265.2",
      "line_index": 265,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "b17da9dc",
      "speaker": "ベス",
      "ja": "あ、でもそれで貴方が興奮するなら、その、構いませんけど……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "268.0",
      "line_index": 268,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "58a13f0f",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "ありがとうベス。それじゃあ動くよ？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "277.0",
      "line_index": 277,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "3e55a0df",
      "speaker": "ベス",
      "ja": "はうっ……！？♥　う、うう……何、これ……ビリって……あうっ！♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "279.0",
      "line_index": 279,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "bcaaf9a9",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "僅かに腰を揺らし、あそこを擦ると甘い声を口から漏らすベス。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "281.0",
      "line_index": 281,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "434c4312",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "思っていた以上にベスは感じやすいようで、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "281.2",
      "line_index": 281,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "434c4312",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "動くたびに声がどんどん大きくなっていく。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "284.0",
      "line_index": 284,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "6332ec95",
      "speaker": "ベス",
      "ja": "ふ、ふ……な、なんだか思っていたのと違って……んっ！♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "284.2",
      "line_index": 284,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "6332ec95",
      "speaker": "ベス",
      "ja": "あう……！？♥　あ♥　そこ、ダメ……んっ！♥　んぅぅぅっ！♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "286.0",
      "line_index": 286,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "a263ab8c",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "亀頭がベスの小さなクリトリスに触れると、ビクンと腰が大きく跳ねる。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "288.0",
      "line_index": 288,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "470151a5",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "ベスは快感から逃れるように腰をくねらせる。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "290.0",
      "line_index": 290,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "224eee13",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "挟み込んだ肉棒がむちむちの太ももに捏ねられ、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "290.2",
      "line_index": 290,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "224eee13",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "それがさらに気持ち良さをもたらしてくる。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "293.0",
      "line_index": 293,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "6809b4e",
      "speaker": "ベス",
      "ja": "そこばかりダメ……ですわ♥　声、出て……う、うううっ！♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "293.2",
      "line_index": 293,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "6809b4e",
      "speaker": "ベス",
      "ja": "あ、ああ……きっきもち……いい……あうっ！♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "296.0",
      "line_index": 296,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "5a9944bb",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "声我慢しなくても大丈夫だよ。外には聞こえないから。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "296.2",
      "line_index": 296,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "5a9944bb",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "もっとベスの可愛い声聞かせてくれ",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "300.0",
      "line_index": 300,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "fcd6fdbc",
      "speaker": "ベス",
      "ja": "あひぃっ！？♥　んあ、おっぱい揉んじゃダメぇえ……ああぁっ！♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "302.0",
      "line_index": 302,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "c99d85f8",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "軽く指に力を入れただけで、全身を震わせるベス。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "304.0",
      "line_index": 304,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "d149a374",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "僅かに開いてきているあそこから、ねっとりとした愛液が溢れる。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "304.2",
      "line_index": 304,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "d149a374",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "それが潤滑油となり、さらに肉棒を擦る動きがスムーズになっていく。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "307.0",
      "line_index": 307,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "3fe26644",
      "speaker": "ベス",
      "ja": "ひ、んひぃ……！♥　ダメ……気持ち良い、気持ち良いよぉ♥　はううっ！♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "309.0",
      "line_index": 309,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "5eec32c0",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "ぐちゅぐちゅと大きな水音が部屋に響き渡る。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "311.0",
      "line_index": 311,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "66fa4c15",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "ベスはそれが自分の愛液だと悟っているのか、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "311.2",
      "line_index": 311,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "66fa4c15",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "恥ずかしさと快感に耐えるように身を固くする。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "313.0",
      "line_index": 313,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "a5fd6d9a",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "そんなベスから少しでも力を抜こうと、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "313.2",
      "line_index": 313,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "a5fd6d9a",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "ツンと勃起している乳首を指先で弾く。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "316.0",
      "line_index": 316,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "8f8dbedc",
      "speaker": "ベス",
      "ja": "んあぁぁっ！♥　ああ、それダメぇ！　快感が余計にぃ……あうっ！！♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "319.0",
      "line_index": 319,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "8fd90940",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "くっ！？　うあ、ベス……くううっ！！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "322.0",
      "line_index": 322,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "ec3c59d3",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "ベスはぎゅっと両脚を閉じ、肉棒に思わぬ快感が走る。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "324.0",
      "line_index": 324,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "b1188503",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "それでも太ももをこじ開けるように肉棒を動かし続け、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "324.2",
      "line_index": 324,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "b1188503",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "ベスの割れ目を何度も往復させる。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "327.0",
      "line_index": 327,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "29039ab1",
      "speaker": "ベス",
      "ja": "うう、これ……もう……うう♥　私、貴族なのにぃ……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "327.2",
      "line_index": 327,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "29039ab1",
      "speaker": "ベス",
      "ja": "平民の貴方に……い、イかされちゃうぅぅぅ……！！♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "330.0",
      "line_index": 330,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "8ee8e273",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "気持ち良くなるのに貴族も平民もないって。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "330.2",
      "line_index": 330,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "8ee8e273",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "俺もそろそろだから……二人で一緒に絶頂しよう",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "334.0",
      "line_index": 334,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "7e55cdb",
      "speaker": "ベス",
      "ja": "んんんっ！♥　ああぁっ！！♥　乳首コリコリダメぇええっ！！♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "334.2",
      "line_index": 334,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "7e55cdb",
      "speaker": "ベス",
      "ja": "あぁっ！　んあ♥　あぁぁっ！♥　ああーっ！♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "336.0",
      "line_index": 336,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "1b259dfe",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "尿道をせり上がってくる精液。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "336.2",
      "line_index": 336,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "1b259dfe",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "それでもベスを絶頂させようと、腰に力を入れ精液を押し込める。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "338.0",
      "line_index": 338,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "51f58f1a",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "快感を堪えながら",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "338.2",
      "line_index": 338,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "51f58f1a",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "ベスの小さな乳首とクリトリスを音を立てながら擦り上げる。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "341.0",
      "line_index": 341,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "3e8944b",
      "speaker": "ベス",
      "ja": "もう……イっちゃう！♥　イっちゃうの！♥　ああぁぁっ！♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "341.2",
      "line_index": 341,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "3e8944b",
      "speaker": "ベス",
      "ja": "イク、イク……イっちゃうーーーっ！！♥♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "372.0",
      "line_index": 372,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "a5a85632",
      "speaker": "ベス",
      "ja": "ふうううっ！♥　んあ、あ……あああーーっ！！♥♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "374.0",
      "line_index": 374,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "82eb424",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "ベスは大きな悲鳴を上げ、全身を捩る。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "375.0",
      "line_index": 375,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "5acafb1a",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "腰がビクンと何度も大きく跳ね、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "375.2",
      "line_index": 375,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "5acafb1a",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "あそこから粘度の高い愛液がどぷりと溢れる。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "378.0",
      "line_index": 378,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "d893ac74",
      "speaker": "ベス",
      "ja": "んぅぅう……♥　あ、熱い……貴方の……でて、る……♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "378.2",
      "line_index": 378,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "d893ac74",
      "speaker": "ベス",
      "ja": "これが精液……んぅぅぅ♥　す、すごい匂い……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "378.4",
      "line_index": 378,
      "inline_index": 4,
      "line_hash": "d893ac74",
      "speaker": "ベス",
      "ja": "頭クラクラしますわ……あうっ♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "381.0",
      "line_index": 381,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "8cef8fb0",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "ふぅ……！　ふぅぅ……！　ベスのおまんこと太ももが気持ち良くて……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "381.2",
      "line_index": 381,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "8cef8fb0",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "何だかたくさん出てしまったよ……こんなに汚してごめんな",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "385.0",
      "line_index": 385,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "1e955c9a",
      "speaker": "ベス",
      "ja": "はぁ♥　はぁぁ……♥　気にする必要はありませんわ……♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "385.2",
      "line_index": 385,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "1e955c9a",
      "speaker": "ベス",
      "ja": "私が望んだことですもの……♥　でもこれで……ん♥　ちゅ……ちゅる……♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "387.0",
      "line_index": 387,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "6ca19207",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "ベスは精液を指で掬うと精液を舐め始める。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "388.0",
      "line_index": 388,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "6763c352",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "その淫らで、それでいて可愛いベスの姿に太ももの間で肉棒が跳ね上がる。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "391.0",
      "line_index": 391,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "ab3b7036",
      "speaker": "ベス",
      "ja": "ふあ♥　貴方のまだ元気みたいですわね……♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "391.2",
      "line_index": 391,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "ab3b7036",
      "speaker": "ベス",
      "ja": "まだまだ私のために出してくれるというのですね……♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "394.0",
      "line_index": 394,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "53c387c3",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "ああ……ベスが可愛すぎてとてもじゃないが一度じゃ満足できそうにない",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "398.0",
      "line_index": 398,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "8a88575",
      "speaker": "ベス",
      "ja": "それならもっとしてくださいまし……♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "398.2",
      "line_index": 398,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "8a88575",
      "speaker": "ベス",
      "ja": "精液がたくさんあることに越したことはありませんわ……♥",
      "zh": ""
