      "key": "507.2",
      "line_index": 507,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "2323d91b",
      "speaker": "ベス",
      "ja": "でもほかの娘にも同じことおっしゃっていませんよね……？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "510.0",
      "line_index": 510,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "24c7dda0",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "い、いや、言ったことはない、と思うけど",
      "zh": ""
    },
